    .page-header.header-filter(data-parallax='true', style="background-image: url('../assets/img/back.png')")
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-12
           center
            h1.title Goodbye notaries.
            h4
              | Authenticating documents is now simple and secure.
            br
            a.btn.btn-danger.btn-raised.btn-lg(href='#beginHere', target='_self')
              |  Begin
    .main.main-raised
      .container
        .section.text-center
          .row
            .col-md-8.ml-auto.mr-auto
              h3.title(style="color: #545454 !important;") We're live in ETH Ropsten and RSK Mainnet!
              h5.description
                | We're proud to bring the first release of our platform in Beta version. Not all functionalities have been
                | implemented yet, so please be mindful when using the service. We currently allow for simple and multi-sig document registrations.
                | Registration and login are not necessary but unlock extra features. See below the benefits of using Certfy.me.
          .features
            .row
              .col-md-4
                .info
                  .icon.icon-info
                    i.material-icons vpn_lock
                  h4.info-title Immutability
                  p
                    | Once you create a registration, it is immutable. We can't even modify it, and we built this platform. This is ideal for proving the validity of documents
                    | and the existence of agreements between parties.
              .col-md-4
                .info
                  .icon.icon-success
                    i.material-icons fingerprint
                  h4.info-title Verifiability
                  p
                    | By registering documents immutably on a blockchain, you can verify that you have been given the correct copy 
                    | or prove the existence of a record at a given point in time.
              .col-md-4
                .info
                  .icon.icon-danger
                    i.material-icons lock
                  h4.info-title Security
                  p
                    | Our platform is backed by the Ethereum blockchain, providing security to the data and the application. Also, by using Proxy contract implementations, we 
                    | can easily upgrade the platform while ensuring the storage persists.
        .section.section-contacts(id='beginHere')
          .row
            .col-md-8.ml-auto.mr-auto
              h2.text-center.title Register your first document
              h4.text-center.description
                | No login necessary. Make sure you have MetaMask installed. (We're currently using Ethereum's Ropsten Network)
              form.contact-formy
                .row
                  .col-md-12
                    .form-group
                      label.bmd-label-floating Document Title
                      input.form-control(type='text', id="title")
                .form-group
                  label.bmd-label-floating Document Description
                  textarea.form-control(type='text', rows='4', id="desc")
                .form-group
                  label.bmd-label-floating Add file
                 input.form-control-file(id='inp' type='file')
                br
                .form-group
                  label.bmd-label-floating Current price per standard registration (gas not included):
                  span(id="stdPrice")
                br
                .form-group
                  label.bmd-label-floating Current price per multi-sig registration (gas not included):
                  span(id="multiPrice")
                br
                br
                .row
                  .col-md-4.ml-auto.mr-auto.text-center
                    button.btn.btn-primary.btn-raised.noreload(onclick="intermediate();")
                      | Register
              br
              center
              #myProgress
               #myBar
              span(id="event") 
